HEADWORD: Tractor-trailer
<hw>Tract"o*r-trail"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a
combination of a tractor{4} hooked up to a trailer, forming a common
type of <isa>truck{7}</isa> used for carrying freight on highways.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Traffic was backed up for miles by a jackknifed
<ex>tractor-trailer</ex>.⟦rdquo⟧⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

